cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.NE, cs.CR 

This paper proposes a novel method for improving uncertainty estimation in deep neural networks. The focus is on machine learning and artificial intelligence (cs.LG, cs.AI), specifically on computer vision (cs.CV) and neural networks (cs.NE). The paper also discusses the detection of adversarial examples, which falls under computer security and cryptography (cs.CR).
